    <!-- What is E-Commerce Supply Chain? -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>What is an E-Commerce Supply Chain?</h2>
      <p>An e-commerce supply chain is the interconnected system that enables the movement of goods in an online retail business. It covers everything from sourcing raw materials or finished products to warehousing, inventory management, order processing, shipping, and returns.</p>
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/1200x400?text=Sourcing+and+Procurement" alt="Sourcing and Procurement">
    </div>

    <!-- How Does It Work? -->
