        <div class="grid-item">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100?text=📊" alt="Inventory">
          <h3>Inventory Management</h3>
          <p>Storing products in warehouses and managing stock levels to prevent shortages or overstocking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100?text=📝" alt="Order Processing">
          <h3>Order Processing</h3>
          <p>Receiving and processing customer orders through an automated system.</p>
